Text:
Not that I wouldn't appreciate your effort of uploading this, but why are all of your videos a few seconds back with the sound?

Kind regards,

Alexey
Thanks, I love Kathy Griffin :) , and Larry King's show is really good :) , too bad I can't get CNN anymore here. :(
